title: Minnehaha 1930's Duplex 1 bed/1 bath. $1425
posting_body: ['Seeking a responsible and respectful tenant for South Mpls duplex.', 'Do you love the Mississippi Greenway and Minnehaha Falls?', 'On the waiting list at Becketwood, and want to live nearby while you wait?', 'Available October 1st, possibly sooner.', "Gorgeous 1930's Craftsman, side by side Duplex.", 'No one above or below!', 'Beautiful, well maintained and beloved duplex, 1 bed/1 bath, hardwood floors, cordless blinds,', 'and1/2 of huge garage with remote.', "Each unit has it's own energy efficient HVAC system, with central air and gas heat, a hot water heater, it's own washer/dryer, and a 700 sq/ft private, dry basement, perfect for crafts, workouts or storage.", 'Landlord covers water, trash, yard and snow service, tenant pays gas and electric.', 'Easy guest parking, no houses across the street.', 'On bus line to light rail.', 'Spitting distance to the Mississippi River green way, 4 blocks to Minnehaha Falls and Sea Salt.', 'Bike or cross-country ski right out the door!', 'No pets, no smoking.', 'Nice professional neighbors.', 'Limited to 1 or 2 residents.', 'Huge historic community garden near by, or garden out back.', 'Deposit $1425, 1 year lease but flexible.', "Need good references, no UD's, will do check credit.", "Close to VA Hospital, Fort Snelling, Airport, U of M, St Kate's, Cub Foods and Lunds.", 'Thank you!']
